{"tid":2358922,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發明咗個物理通便裝置 解決便秘問題","createTime":"2021-01-08T13:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T13:23:07.000Z","uid":51346,"like":889,"dislike":248,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"31d1c5d6cdf8df2a411215117596dd7fc3b15212","tid":2358922,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:09:37.000Z","msg":"有時啲屎太硬 塞住條腸屙唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果我哋吞粒鐵球落肚 再用磁石喺體外推郁佢<br />\n<br />\n咪可以推啲屎出嚟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gcE75Ln.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgcE75Ln.gif&h=bcc93370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係有個問題 就係粒鐵球太大會吞唔落<br />\n<br />\n太細又可能會咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gD9DsYX.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgD9DsYX.gif&h=0215ac79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有局部嘅屎推到出嚟<br />\n<br />\n所以我諗到用呢樣嘢代替<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q1U4oxx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq1U4oxx.gif&h=b9aaf29e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n眾所周知 爆丸一放近鐵 就會爆開 <br />\n套用喺呢個情況上面 一爆開 表面面積就增加<br />\n更利於抓實啲硬屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRctQB8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRctQB8.gif&h=ec02def6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n爆丸通便法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/juqGraC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjuqGraC.gif&h=9b776b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n推完啲屎出嚟洗下粒爆丸 <br />\n又可以俾下位有需要嘅巴打用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7840de257f0d926ee87a6089c47652d30a2e03c8","tid":2358922,"uid":51346,"like":32,"dislike":9,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:09:44.000Z","msg":"幫p牌巴推<br />\n十八區區報默默耕耘咁大件事冇人講！？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2358794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2358794</a>"},{"pid":"3c2a9b38dbc38f0445b0e9571b668a6870ec762e","tid":2358922,"uid":201299,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:09:54.000Z","msg":"gif"},{"pid":"3839761dbadf9419712d31e544745ea3ec084d90","tid":2358922,"uid":374518,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe2a636d3935a221c0b43c67f3839972d366509","tid":2358922,"uid":16425,"like":147,"dislike":7,"score":140,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:10:08.000Z","msg":"痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af86fb85ebc0b229e9c06ad4c19b74bb33487c10","tid":2358922,"uid":161685,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:10:10.000Z","msg":"CLS"},{"pid":"a979d289a80506f70cd265dc39c11089d245b9a6","tid":2358922,"uid":222328,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:10:41.000Z","msg":"通屎眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50dec833e11856682f6dd0a02fcde2323f6fe2b0","tid":2358922,"uid":285514,"like":174,"dislike":6,"score":168,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:10:49.000Z","msg":"腸穿肚爛大法"},{"pid":"cce07d56c095e229518005b01c682a02230c5d53","tid":2358922,"uid":310343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9dddaf4e33cb1c0a61fb324b93987a1c85051e","tid":2358922,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T13:11:12